{"tid":1290902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急呼籲：最後三日向選委會提出反DQ區議會侯選人","createTime":"2019-07-06T16:05:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T04:16:35.000Z","uid":268073,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"4f2f1b2b84260b887495c58f4bc7f97eac5becd2","tid":1290902,"uid":268073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:05:43.000Z","msg":"今年區議會侯選人提名安排有意見，請盡公民義務向選委會提交，七月十日截止啦。<br />\n<br />\n(2019區議會選舉活動指引）<br />\n<br />\n第三章 提名候選人程序<br />\n3.1 在區議會選舉中獲提名的候選人須符合兩部分的 要求。就第一部分，候選人要符合《區議會條例》第 20 條 關於獲提名為候選人的資格，以及不會因該條例第 21 條所 述的情況而喪失獲提名為候選人或當選為議員的資格。至 於第二部分是關於法定聲明的要求，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">《區議會條例》第 34 條規定，候選人須在提名表格中作出一項聲明，示明該 人會擁護《基本法》和保證效忠香港特別行政區。</span>根據法例，候選人的提名是否有效，完全是由選舉主任作出決定，選管會無權並一向沒有參與，亦不會給予任何意見。<br />\n<br />\n3.2 根據《區議會選舉程序規例》第 19 條，如選舉主 任決定某提名無效，選舉主任必須在有關提名表格上批註 他的決定及作出該決定的理由，並根據該規例第 14 條，供 公眾查閱。如任何人士因為其在某選舉中喪失作為候選人 的資格，可根據《區議會條例》第 49 條，提出選舉呈請質 疑選舉結果。<br />\n<br />\n選舉主任有咩資格同知識去判定侯選人係咪真誠宣誓先？等到選舉呈請都大局已定。仲有，呢個根本唔係選舉主任責任，選舉主任係公務員，係中立的。要DQ侯選人係政治問題，就留番俾㐂婆做，唔好射個鑊俾中立的公務員。<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲打唔好因爲無開記者會就俾選委會過到關。未來仲有漫漫長路要大家繼續幫手守護香港，請盡公民義務向選委會提交，七月十日截止啦。<br />\n<br />\n自己香港自己救。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019區議會選舉活動指引<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/2019dc_guide_prop.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.hk%2Fch%2Fdistco%2F2019dc_guide_prop.htm&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=4ab47a22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/2019dc_guide_prop.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n區議會選舉活動建議指引公眾諮詢今日展開<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/11/P2019061100462.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201906%2F11%2FP2019061100462.htm&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=4f40ac6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/11/P2019061100462.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n市民可於七月十日或之前，將書面意見寄交至灣仔港灣道二十五號海港中心十樓選管會秘書處，亦可透過傳真（2511 1682）或電郵（eacenq@eac.hk）遞交。逾期遞交的意見將不獲考慮。"},{"pid":"ef3bbab27666b61e72eee57655e4937defe48a9e","tid":1290902,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:07:42.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ee740f476f7e927f45c50a5447868582c6a302f8","tid":1290902,"uid":272775,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:11:26.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n一人一信反DQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3分鐘就寫好！<br />\n<a href=\"https://271467.typeform.com/to/MTUjKV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F271467.typeform.com%2Fto%2FMTUjKV&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zR3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=781984d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://271467.typeform.com/to/MTUjKV</a>"},{"pid":"605e693a52897328a81e3a1aa72b5015082942d9","tid":1290902,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:18:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de06a3b5e9cd3d4b3969e7bf2ca58524640f4158","tid":1290902,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:18:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f1dcf303a6da89a548d559eecda9a808f8544b0","tid":1290902,"uid":61625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:19:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89408739f69c9c2991fab78dfe636379b3ff7d12","tid":1290902,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9614394688c05a7d68b1f64a45aedcf9e57c0800","tid":1290902,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T16:22:58.000Z","msg":"我冇野講呀"},{"pid":"ac430488dde33b4a0c34fa23da65597732e11374","tid":1290902,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:00:56.000Z","msg